in MUNKÁCS.

221
00:11:25,626 --> 00:11:26,295
⟨yo.⟩

222
00:11:28,596 --> 00:11:30,480
deys iz mayn kale-bild,

223
00:11:31,144 --> 00:11:38,410
vos ⟨iz⟩ oykhet ⟨f- i⟩n⟩ toyznt nayn hundert zekhtsiker yor in MUNKÁCS. ikh bin aleyn.

224
00:11:43,193 --> 00:11:44,570
UNK

225
00:11:44,745 --> 00:11:46,663
dey- deys iz di bild

226
00:11:47,007 --> 00:11:52,361
vos mir ho'mir gemakht in toyznt nayn hundert akhtsiker yor in Amerike, in Bruklin:

227
00:11:52,361 --> 00:11:57,060
mayn shvoger, Ignats, di shvester, Miryem,

228
00:11:57,570 --> 00:11:59,893
ikh bin dort, un mayn man,

229
00:12:00,642 --> 00:12:03,380
un dos kind, Malkele.

230
00:12:06,700 --> 00:12:08,578
deys iz di khasene

231
00:12:08,578 --> 00:12:10,924
fun mayn bruder's zun,

232
00:12:10,924 --> 00:12:14,439
ey- in eyn toyznt nayn ⟨hundert⟩ dray un zibetsiker yor.

233
00:12:14,513 --> 00:12:16,279
dort iz Malke,

234
00:12:17,955 --> 00:12:21,712
.. vi azoy heyst er nor...? Yitskhok,

235
00:12:22,005 --> 00:12:23,731
Didi, di kale,

236
00:12:23,731 --> 00:12:25,593
Ari, der khosn,

237
00:12:25,887 --> 00:12:29,450
un mayn, un di shvegerin, Zhuzhi,

238
00:12:29,450 --> 00:12:31,179
un der bruder, Moyshe.

239
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,254
vu?

240
00:12:33,266 --> 00:12:35,400
in ⟨DETROIT⟩.

241
00:12:37,952 --> 00:12:43,040
deys iz a bar-mitsve fun mayn shvester's zun,

242
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,656
fun an eynikl,

243
00:12:44,656 --> 00:12:49,303
in eyn toyznt nayn hundert nayntsiker yor, befor zi iz geshtorbn.

244
00:12:50,625 --> 00:12:55,570
dort iz UNK Meyerko,

245
00:12:56,076 --> 00:12:59,968
Borekh, der zun, Volvi,

246
00:13:00,767 --> 00:13:02,685
Zalmi, der zun,

247
00:13:04,277 --> 00:13:07,020
an eynikl, Gitele,

248
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:11,870
 Yoli, di sh- a shnur,

249
00:13:12,006 --> 00:13:13,654
Anye, a shnur,

250
00:13:14,065 --> 00:13:17,062
Piri, a shnur, Mendl, der zun,

251
00:13:20,595 --> 00:13:24,140
UNK, MIKEY, dos eynikl,

252
00:13:25,422 --> 00:13:27,154
Malkele...

253
00:13:27,784 --> 00:13:30,060
di ze ikh nisht...

254
00:13:31,294 --> 00:13:32,435
un ikh.

255
00:13:33,555 --> 00:13:34,278
vu?

256
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:37,180
 in Bruklin.

